org.livingdoc.engine.fixtures

Interface Fixture<T extends TestData>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DecisionTableFixtureWrapper, ScenarioFixtureWrapper, ScenarioNoFixture

    public Fixture<T extends TestData>

    This interface is the basis for all specialized fixture classes. It wraps or represents a fixture and offers an execute function to execute it with some test data

    • Method Detail

      • execute

        @NotNull
TestDataResult<T> execute(@NotNull
                                   T testData)

        Executes the fixture class with the give testData

        Parameters:
        testData - A test data instance that can be mapped to the fixture
        Returns:
        A TestDataResult for the execution
